      </html:li>


      
 <html:li
style="list-style-type: &quot;(ùõΩ) &quot;">
        a filtered complex <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[(K_{A\otimes \mathbb {Q}},W)\in \operatorname {Ob}\mathrm {D}^+F(A\otimes \mathbb {Q})]]></fr:tex> (for an <fr:em>increasing</fr:em> filtration <fr:tex
