display="inline"><![CDATA[K]]></fr:tex> is a Hodge complex (resp. cohomological Hodge complex) of weight <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>, then <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[K[m]]]></fr:tex> is a Hodge complex (resp. cohomological Hodge complex) of weight <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n+m]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
