display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>, the system consisting of the complex <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Gr}_n^W(K_{A\otimes \mathbb {Q}})\in \operatorname {Ob}\mathrm {D}^+(A\otimes \mathbb {Q})]]></fr:tex>, the complex <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Gr}_n^W(K_\mathbb {C})\in \operatorname {Ob}\mathrm {D}^+F(\mathbb {C})]]></fr:tex> filtered by <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[F]]></fr:tex>, and the isomorphism
        <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[           \operatorname {Gr}_n^W(\alpha )\colon            \operatorname {Gr}_n^W(K_{A\otimes \mathbb {Q}})\otimes \mathbb {C}           \simeq  \operatorname {Gr}_n^W(K_\mathbb {C}),         ]]></fr:tex>
        is a Hodge <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[(A\otimes \mathbb {Q})]]></fr:tex>-complex of weight <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree></fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
